Steven M. Fludder

Age : 56Public asset : 1,900,000 USDLinked companies :  Ocean Power Technologies Inc -  alpha-En Corporation 





Summary 



Mr. Steven M. Fludder is Chief Executive Officer at alpha-En Corp.He is on the Board of Directors at Ocean Power Technologies, Inc. Mr. Fludder was previously employed as Chief Executive Officer-Energy & Water Business by AECOM Technology Corp., Vice President & Head-Marketing by Samsung Engineering Co., Ltd., Vice President-Global Sales by GE Water & Process Technologies Co, President & Chief Executive Officer by GE Energy China, Vice President & Head-Ecomagination by General Electric Co., and President-Power Systems Division by Hanwha Techwin Co., Ltd.He received his undergraduate degree from Providence College, a graduate degree from Columbia University and a graduate degree from Massachusetts Institute of Technology.



